Package com.vmworld.repository

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BankingDatabase
    Simulates an in-memory database that holds all customer records for the banking application.
    Uses static array to simulate persistent storage.
    CustomerRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing customer data operations.
    Handles creation, ID generation and duplicate checks
    TransactionRepository
    Repository class handling transaction-related operations.
    Manages deposits, withdrawals, balance checks and history.
